    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, ensuring a reliable driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. This is a solid, dependable car ready for its next owner.",
