    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine is currently running roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Physically, the exterior has several large dents and fading paint, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car suited for someone with the tools and time for a full restoration.",
